lable coincident microwave observations up to 190 GHz (with observations from Tropical Rainfall Measuring Mission's (TRMM) Microwave Imager (TMI), Microwave Humidity Sounder (MHS) and Special Sensor Microwave Imager/Sounder (SSMI/S)) using the $\chi$ 2 test. Good agreement is obtained with all observations provided special care is taken to represent the scattering properties of the snow and graupel species.},
